{"tid":723893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"成隊阿根廷,出曬啲大牌球員踢都好過阿甲啲垃圾啦","createTime":"2018-06-30T16:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T16:59:57.000Z","uid":4701,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d924919b9b6893bc1d549af03064c17207ef90","tid":723893,"uid":4701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"其實阿根廷今屆場場都係靠個人能力同-6入波架啦<br />\n成隊波都冇化學作用,又冇陣型,次次都唔同人<br />\n既然係咁,出曬美斯,迪馬,阿古路,希古恩,戴巴拿算啦<br />\n個個都係得分好手,真係俾佢地自由發揮,踢個人能力都好過出啲阿甲連波都未識傳既人啦<br />\n輸緊2球,出啲攻力強啲人踢真係咁難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係阿根廷球迷都睇到嬲,前面咁靚既牌面都發揮唔到,好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad61b1c166ed72d41d977fe9b4d3e9bd7eab0d32","tid":723893,"uid":72475,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"前面勁有咩用 一個反擊就一球"},{"pid":"e4cdb9fcbde0f9327fa62cec892fe6ce6c5534ac","tid":723893,"uid":34513,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ad61b1c166ed72d41d977fe9b4d3e9bd7eab0d32","tid":723893,"uid":72475,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"前面勁有咩用 一個反擊就一球"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"呢家唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea87c05fc510e15cb388f575fd397be5413923fd","tid":723893,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"個美沙真係最大笑話來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e501f01eb35c57127214cdd0f76c024d2ffa1516","tid":723893,"uid":39889,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-